{"tid":2513893,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"ITZY留真妝髮一換，直接同時撞臉三位女星！李沇熹、韓韶禧、孫娜恩","createTime":"2021-05-03T01:52:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T02:15:54.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bf88f247e656a528f4719c153b0a0419a3ecd502","tid":2513893,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T01:52:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_f6e071acece48d026663b7c5eef6e346/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-05-02/135236-905143.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_f6e071acece48d026663b7c5eef6e346%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-05-02%2F135236-905143.jpg&h=625e4255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n留真辨識度本來就很高，但只要換一下妝髮，就會有不同感覺，四位都是美女啊～！（各種風格直接駕馭）<br />\n<br />\n人氣女團 ITZY 登上熱門節目《認識的哥哥》引爆了不少話題性，而開場在介紹時，留真分享了網友認為她自拍後，會撞臉女星們的小故事。<br />\n<br />\n留真在變換不同髮型、妝容和表情時，就能展現出不同的風格！早先被引爆話題的是【車裡的女生到底是韓韶禧還是ITZY留真？已經像到快分不清了！】<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_481f7471cda5eb02b3cf1e83d3d38d97/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-05-02/135236-905144.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_481f7471cda5eb02b3cf1e83d3d38d97%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-05-02%2F135236-905144.jpg&h=3ef70123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車裡的這位，其實是留真喔！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_93f518fb18d460dda7fc6c9d176085cb/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-05-02/135236-905145.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_93f518fb18d460dda7fc6c9d176085cb%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-05-02%2F135236-905145.png&h=323c5b4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼節目上的比對圖，同樣擁有嫵媚的雙眼！<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_d69dd4c6c20a66dee640166ebe7029f8/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-05-02/135236-905146.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_d69dd4c6c20a66dee640166ebe7029f8%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-05-02%2F135236-905146.png&h=0b304884&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼還有人說過她像李沇熹，徐章焄驚呼：根本是同個人吧！？<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_654a8f3de4bac9e69154c6428d7c7f00/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-05-02/135236-905147.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_654a8f3de4bac9e69154c6428d7c7f00%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-05-02%2F135236-905147.png&h=1e4ddc61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_dda9d1a15e20fcb6832d6b61472564e9/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-05-02/135236-905148.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_dda9d1a15e20fcb6832d6b61472564e9%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-05-02%2F135236-905148.png&h=7be38678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼然後，在練習生時期，彩領曾說過留真跟孫娜恩也很相像。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_47f47c8d6a222e26d1ddc1b7aa210019/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-05-02/135236-905149.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_47f47c8d6a222e26d1ddc1b7aa210019%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-05-02%2F135236-905149.png&h=ced4f3e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此外，留真也被稱作是ITZY的姜鎬童，力氣超大，直接在節目上示範背起兩位成員，相當厲害！"},{"pid":"593cc32ea4a35c82f6aa95072b108d8917c251c9","tid":2513893,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T01:53:03.000Z","msg":"戀愛留真&hellip;"},{"pid":"51c52428840e70203e56ee1ba337a7a92cce4bfd","tid":2513893,"uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T01:54:11.000Z","msg":"邊個黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d9c68854d85e131f74fac45ce272f52f38e9ab","tid":2513893,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"593cc32ea4a35c82f6aa95072b108d8917c251c9","tid":2513893,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T01:53:03.000Z","msg":"戀愛留真&hellip;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi